snippet.title: Chess + Poker = Choker game app
snippet.description:
📱 INSTALL CHOKER ON GOOGLE PLAY STORE  http://bit.ly/ChokerPlayStore
📱 INSTALL CHOKER ON APPLE APP STORE http://bit.ly/ChokerAppStore

Choker is a unique blend of chess and poker creating a whole new game experience.

Choker is a just-for-fun, free-to-play app available on the Google Play and Apple App stores.

FREE Rules Download  http://bit.ly/ChokerGameRules
